Dia. 01 It is Sente, but...
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's descending move at 1 is sente against the corner. White has to answer at 2.
\par
\par If White doesn't play at 2, Black plays there and White is captured in the corner.
\par
\par It shows that the \cf1\b value of a sente \cf0\b0 is even \cf1\b higher if it has also connection to life and death\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par However Black 1 is not the best move.
\par
\par
\par }
