Dia. 02  Correct Answer-Hane and Connection
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's hane at 1 and the connection at 3 is the correct answer. White has to defend at 4 for living.
\par
\par White's territory was reduced more than in the previous diagram.
\par
\par If a sente has effect on a group's life and death like here, it is called \cf1\b absolute sente\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
