Dia. 03 What Kind of Endgame?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par What kind of endgame sequence is the hane and connection at 1 and 3?
\par
\par If White has to answer, it would be sente endgame.
\par However if White doesn't have to answer, it is gote endgame.
\par
\par }
