Dia. 04 Gote Endgame
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White is alive now, so he can play elsewhere.
\par If Black plays at A White plays at B, if Black plays at B, White plays at A.
\par Therefore Black's hane-connection sequence was \cf1\b gote endgame\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
